id: pm-j1fj
title: "Project profile author-time validation: lintProjectProfile + assertProjectProfile + pm profile lint"
description: "Profiles (defineProjectProfile / api.registerProfile) have no author-time consistency check, unlike the extension surface (lintExtensionBlueprint/assertExtensionBlueprint/preflightExtension). Problems only surface at 'pm profile apply' (config-knob errors, fail-fast) or never (a workflow transition referencing an undeclared status silently stages a dead/unreachable rule; a workflow governing an undeclared item type; duplicate type/status/field keys with silent last-wins upsert). Add a pure core lintProjectProfile(profile) returning graded findings (error/warning) across every dimension, the SDK assertProjectProfile test helper, an author-facing describeProjectProfile describe primitive (parity with describeExtensionBlueprint, dedupes the CLI compositionOf), and a 'pm profile lint [name]' CLI subcommand + pm_profile MCP action so operators/agents can validate builtin or extension-contributed profiles before applying. Completes the profile author->register->describe->lint->apply lifecycle."
type: Feature
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[5]: "area:config","area:schema",living-map,pm-cli,sdk
created_at: "2026-06-29T19:03:29.843Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-30T05:34:40.038Z"
author: claude-code-agent
acceptance_criteria: "lintProjectProfile pure + 100% covered; graded findings (error/warning) with stable codes across profile/types/statuses/fields/workflows/config/templates/packages; assertProjectProfile throws on errors (strict also on warnings); describeProjectProfile dedupes CLI compositionOf; 'pm profile lint' wired into CLI dispatch, MCP pm_profile (lint action), completion (bash/zsh/fish), contracts full.json; builtin agile/ops/research profiles lint clean; docs + CHANGELOG updated."
parent: pm-8jdc
resolution: "Shipped author-time project-profile validation: pure core lintProjectProfile with graded error/warning findings, SDK assertProjectProfile, describeProjectProfile parity primitive, and the `pm profile lint [name]` CLI subcommand + pm_profile lint MCP action. Merged in PR #404 (5e209103); this closeout records the lineage after the two deferred follow-ups (pm-zumn, pm-fq80) were also completed."
expected_result: "Operators and agents can validate builtin or extension-contributed profiles before applying, completing the profile author->register->describe->lint->apply lifecycle with errors that break apply and warnings for suspicious-but-valid cross-references."
actual_result: "PR #404 delivered core/profile/profile-lint.ts (475 lines) + profile-describe.ts, SDK assertProjectProfile/describeProjectProfile, CLI `pm profile lint`, MCP pm_profile lint action, contracts (full.json + tool schema), and docs; builtin agile/ops/research lint clean; 100% coverage. Deferred MCP follow-ups pm-zumn (extension-aware built-in actions) and pm-fq80 (action-scoped name descriptions) are now closed in feat/mcp-extension-aware-builtin-actions."
